A frustrated customer standing in a sleek, futuristic telecommunications retail store, bathed in harsh neon pink and electric blue lighting. The store interior features holographic displays and glowing circuit-board patterns on walls. The customer is caught in a maze of floating bureaucratic forms, translucent data screens, and tangled fiber optic cables that spiral around them like a trap. Robotic service kiosks surround the person, each pointing in different contradictory directions. The atmosphere conveys technological advancement clashing with absurd red tape—gleaming surfaces and advanced tech contrasted with the human's exasperated body language. Reflective floors, rain-streaked windows showing a dystopian cityscape outside. Cyberpunk style with dramatic lighting, high contrast shadows, and a color palette of magenta, cyan, and deep purple.
